							<h2 id='books_not_returned'><a href="#books_not_returned">Books Not Returned By Due Date/Automatic Extensions and Buyouts</a></h2>
							<p>
							If your book is not returned by the end of your initial rental period, and you have not otherwise extended your rental period, you will automatically be charged for a 7 day extension at the same daily rate of your rental.* If your book has not been returned by the end of this first automatic 7 day extension, you will automatically be charged for a second 7 day extension, and thereafter you will continue to be charged for recurring 7 day extensions after each due date passes.  These automatic 7 day extensions will continue until the book is returned, or the book becomes subject to buyout at the buyout price in one of the three ways listed below.
							</p>
							<p>
							The buyout price equals the list (new) price of the book as set by the publisher plus any applicable sales tax, minus what you’ve already paid to rent the book, including any paid rental extensions.
							</p>
							<p>
							A rental buyout occurs in one of three ways: (1) you may elect a buyout at any time by going to the Extensions/Buyouts section and selecting the buyout option; (2) a buyout will be deemed to have occurred if the amount you have paid (or owe) for a rental, including extensions, is greater than the book’s buyout price (in which case you will be charged the buyout price only); or (3) a buyout will be deemed to have occurred if the book has not been returned after two automatic 7-day extension periods and you fail to pay all applicable extension fees (i.e. your credit/debit card is declined), in which case you will be charged the buyout price. Once you pay the buyout price of a book, it becomes your property.
							</p>
							<p>
							If you have not returned the book by the due date and we are unable to charge your credit/debit card, it is your responsibility to pay the fee immediately.  You will be notified via email if your credit/debit card was declined and have 15 days to pay this fee before your account is turned over to a third-party collection agency.
							<em>
							All accounts sent to collections are subject to an additional $50.00 fee.
